description:
This app is invites you to relive the nostalgic curated sets of DJ Edertech.
This app is invites you to relive the curated DJ sets of DJ Edertech, a devoted enthusiast of old-school music.

Immerse yourself in the nostalgic beats spanning various music genres, including techno, house, breakbeat, jungle/drum & bass, synth-pop, industrial, rock, soul, disco, funk, and more.

DJ Edertech, a DJ since 1989 and a skilled Software Developer, is the mastermind behind this app. The app offers a glimpse into his artistry, sharing curated sets that invite you to relive the golden era of music.
- Explore a rich spectrum of genres.
- Enjoy a seamless, immersive musical experience.
